Letâ€™s take an example for exploring this section. Following is the code in C language to calculate the area of circle whose radius is 5.

Run
#include<stdio.h>
#define PI 3.1416
float area (float r);
int main(void)
{
//Example of variables
float r = 5;
printf("Area: %.2f",area(r)); // This statement will print two digit after the point
return 0;
}

//Example of function
float area(float r)
{
//example of statements & Expression
return PI * r * r;
}
